arts.ttl: Valencia halts Getafe’s super start in La Liga
arts.sum: Arnaut Danjuma got his first goal for Valencia and club stalwart Mouctar Diakhaby was man of the match as they ended Getafe’s fine start to La Liga by 3-0 on Friday. In a matchup of newly promoted sides, Elche beat visiting Levante 2-0.

There is a shock leader after two games in LaLiga, with Villarreal sitting pretty at the summit after winning their opening fixtures by an aggregate score of 7-0, leaving them ahead of Barcelona and Real Madrid on goal difference. 

Another exciting weekend in the Spanish top flight can be expected and we have previewed all 10 matches below.
